3.709+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12480120/comment/12932994","id":"12932994","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=gustavonalle","name":"gustavonalle","emailAddress":"gustavonalle at gmail dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"G Fernandes","active":true},"body":"One option is to pass the type/precision as extra parameters: \r\n\r\n./bin/mahout lucene.vector -d ~/solr/data/index/ -o vectors.vec -t d.dic -f text -i articleId  --idFieldType long --idFieldPrecision 4","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=gustavonalle","name":"gustavonalle","emailAddress":"gustavonalle at gmail dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"G Fernandes","active":true},"created":"2010-11-17T15:49:18.684+0000","updated":"2010-11-17T15:50:18.160+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12480120/comment/13037246","id":"13037246","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=srowen","name":"srowen","emailAddress":"srowen at gmail dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=srowen&avatarId=10104","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=srowen&avatarId=10104","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=srowen&avatarId=10104","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=srowen&avatarId=10104"},"displayName":"Sean Owen","active":true},"body":"I am not sure that is the issue. The stack trace shows a different error. It's trying to serialize a NamedVector which has no name (and I don't know why).\r\n\r\nI propose that we take a step to repair the issue by:\r\n\r\n1. Write an empty string, not null, in this case, even if it shouldn't happen. It at least avoids a failure.\r\n2. Make NamedVector never accept null. This may punt the NPE elsewhere, but will show its cause.\r\n\r\nYou both seem to understand the other issue with Solr and precision. It seems a little ugly to go so far as to work around with a command-line arg, but I don't know well enough to have a strong opinion. Is this something that anyone has any suggested patch for?","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=srowen","name":"srowen","emailAddress":"srowen at gmail dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=srowen&avatarId=10104","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=srowen&avatarId=10104","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=srowen&avatarId=10104","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=srowen&avatarId=10104"},"displayName":"Sean Owen","active":true},"created":"2011-05-21T02:52:28.284+0000","updated":"2011-05-21T02:52:28.284+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12480120/comment/13042689","id":"13042689","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=hudson","name":"hudson","emailAddress":"jira at apache dot org","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"h